text: Gorodskoy () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Dzhidzhikhablskoye Rural Settlement of Teuchezhsky District, the Republic of Adygea, Russia. The population was 297 as of 2018. There are 7 streets.Карта хутора Городской в Республике Адыгее == Ethnicity == The khutor is inhabited by Russians, Ukrainians and Adygheans. == References == Category:Rural localities in Teuchezhsky District
title: Gorodskoy
